idite na zapad!

1316
03:17:33,737 --> 03:17:36,737
Kjuzo, Kikucijo, na istok!

1317
03:19:17,507 --> 03:19:20,507
Kacuširo! Rikici!

1318
03:19:20,644 --> 03:19:23,479
Istok!
Idite na istok!

1319
03:19:23,480 --> 03:19:26,480
Istok!

1320
03:19:42,399 --> 03:19:44,633
Umukni!

1321
03:19:44,634 --> 03:19:47,634
Vrisni, i mrtva si!

1322
03:20:34,250 --> 03:20:35,617
Uspeli smo!

1323
03:20:35,618 --> 03:20:37,119
Uspeli smo !

1324
03:20:37,120 --> 03:20:40,120
Idu na istok!

1325
03:20:55,204 --> 03:20:58,204
Kacuširo, povuci se!

1326
03:21:00,109 --> 03:21:03,109
Proklet bio!

1327
03:21:04,080 --> 03:21:07,080
Kikucijo!

1328
03:21:41,684 --> 03:21:44,684
Kikucijo!

1329
03:21:54,197 --> 03:21:57,266
Gde su banditi?

1330
03:21:57,467 --> 03:22:00,467
Svi su mrtvi!

1331
03:22:17,753 --> 03:22:20,753
Još jednom smo, preživeli.

1332
03:25:58,774 --> 03:26:02,444
A na kraju, i ovu
smo bitku izgubili.

1333
03:26:03,378 --> 03:26:05,446
Šta?

